  "remarks": "ODK-Ufa Engine-Building Production Association (ODK-UMPO) is Russia’s largest gas turbine engine manufacturer and a key subsidiary of the State-owned United Engine Corporation (UEC), which plays a central role in the country’s military-industrial complex. During the Army-2024 military forum, ODK-UMPO made a deal on a 27,5 billion rouble injection from Rostec State Corporation to support its ongoing operations, further reinforcing its strategic importance.",
